				\begin{document}$-dI_{\mathit{FC}}/dV_{\mathit{RPA}}$\end{document} and was observed to be stable with time. The RPA was moved into the beam approximately 20 cm above the DIS aperture at the beginning, middle, and end of each procedure and the beam current measured at VRPA=0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
