				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$4\times 10^{5}$\end{document} electrons/pulse and sweeping MCP voltage while recording the count rate. The MCP operating point voltage was fixed ∼50–100V\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
