				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\sim 50\mbox{--}100~\mbox{V}$\end{document} higher than that at which the count rate in the lowest gain pixel plateaued. In the case of DIS FM14 sensor head 1, the MCP operating voltage was chosen to be −2250V\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
